Repeat: p2, sl 1 wyib, k3, sl 1 wyib, k2
k2, sl 1 wyif, p3, sl 1 wyif, k2

p2, drop first sl-st to front of work, sl nxt 3 sts, drop second sl-st to front; then holding the 3 knit sts on right-hand needle pick up the first dropped st on left-hand needle; then sl the 3 knit sts back to left-hand needle; then with point of right-hand needle pick up the second dropped st and place it on left-hand needle, k5, p2
